#

Beef and Beet Borshch

110 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEastern European

Description

A hearty and colorful Eastern European soup packed with tender beef and sweet beets, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beef stew meat: 1 lb
  • beets: 3 medium
  • potatoes: 2 medium
  • carrots: 1 large
  • onion: 1 large
  • cabbage: 1/2 small head
  • garlic: 3 cloves
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • bay leaves: 2
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • dill: fresh or dried, for garnish
  • sour cream: for serving
